Class Summary
CompetitorPositionOffsetData An instance of this class represents an offset position for a Competitor.

CompetitorPositionSnappedData An instance of this class represents a snapped position for a Competitor.
ControlPointPositionData An instance of this class represents a position for a Control Point (or one of its two buoys/marks).
DataController The main class for data subscription/retrieval.
EventLocationData This class contains information about the location of an event, including the event URL and the database name.
